00:48:23,483 --> 00:48:24,860
invalidate the trade.

826
00:48:28,113 --> 00:48:29,740
This is the Dreams!

827
00:48:30,699 --> 00:48:34,286
-This is the Dreams.
-This is the Dreams!

828
00:48:34,369 --> 00:48:37,456
