-That's a relief.

829
00:48:38,498 --> 00:48:40,709
-Nice.
-Goodness.

830
00:48:41,376 --> 00:48:43,337
This turned out very well.

831
00:48:43,420 --> 00:48:48,675
KANG DOO-KI

832
00:49:00,187 --> 00:49:01,063
Hey.

833
00:49:02,981 --> 00:49:05,776
We boycotted our training because of you.

834
00:49:05,859 --> 00:49:08,654
How could you be so shameless
and train by yourself?

835
00:49:08,737 --> 00:49:11,198
Right. It's a bit of a cheap move.

836
00:49:11,865 --> 00:49:14,826
Are you trying to make
30 wins or something?

837
00:49:15,661 --> 00:49:16,620
Welcome back.

838
00:49:18,330 --> 00:49:19,623
Whether I'm here or not,

839
00:49:20,123 --> 00:49:22,334
