840
00:49:23,293 --> 00:49:24,836
Why didn't you train?

841
00:49:24,920 --> 00:49:26,129
-We should.
-Yes.

842
00:49:26,213 --> 00:49:27,756
Let's train together.

843
00:49:27,839 --> 00:49:29,257
-Let's go!
-Yes!

844
00:49:29,341 --> 00:49:31,218
Here we go.

845
00:49:35,722 --> 00:49:38,392
Kang Doo-ki...

846
00:49:38,475 --> 00:49:40,977
Doo-ki!

847
00:49:49,736 --> 00:49:50,862
Manager Yoon.

848
00:49:51,822 --> 00:49:54,074
