853
00:50:01,915 --> 00:50:03,875
by buying us meat and drinks from now on.

854
00:50:04,793 --> 00:50:07,212
You should learn how to act

855
00:50:07,295 --> 00:50:09,673
like nothing happened, okay?

856
00:50:09,756 --> 00:50:10,674
You should learn.

857
00:50:12,300 --> 00:50:13,176
Get your hand off.

858
00:50:13,885 --> 00:50:14,720
It's gross.

859
00:50:14,803 --> 00:50:16,596
Let's go to training, Mr. Yoon.

860
00:50:17,472 --> 00:50:19,182
